review_text:
(Translated by Google) Water games, children's modules, large picnic area. Ice rinks in winter. Baseball field.

(Original)
Jeux d'eau, modules pour enfants, grand terrain pour pique-nique. Patinoires en hiver. Terrain de baseball.

(Translated by Google) The outdoor rink was closed today, yesterday it was open and there were a few kids playing and having fun but the next day it is closed due to COVID19 but the rink is OUTDOOR !!!

(Original)
La patinoire extérieure était fermée aujourd'hui,  hier il était ouvert et il y avait quelques enfants qui jouent et s'amusent mais le lendemain c'est  fermée à cause de COVID19 mais la patinoire est EXTÉRIEURE !!!

(Translated by Google) Park that needs love ...

(Original)
Parc qui a besoin d'amour...

(Translated by Google) Hockey rink and open skating rink :)

(Original)
Patinoire pour hockey et patinoire pour patin libre :)
